ence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705193,"age":14,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705195,"age":59,"year":"1382","julianDay":2225826,"title":"Wycliffe's Bible","description":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Sarah Tilliard was born in 1323, in Lancashire, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Robert de Tilliard. She married Adam de Urswick about 1295. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in Strickland Ketel, Westmorland, England."},"et":{"1323–":"1323–Surnud","1323–Female":"1323–Surnud","1262–1340":"1262–1340","1302–1401":"1302–1401","1252–1282":"1252–1282","1337":"1337","1401":"1401","1302":"1302","1323":"1323","1453":"1453","1252":"1252","1340":"1340","1262":"1262","1382":"1382","1282":"1282","1328":"1328","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Strickland Ketel, Westmorland, England":"Strickland Ketel, Westmorland, England"},"fi":{"1323–":"1323–Kuollut","1323–Female":"1323–Kuollut","1262–1340":"1262–1340","1302–1401":"1302–1401","1252–1282":"1252–1282","1337":"1337","1401":"1401","1302":"1302","1323":"1323","1453":"1453","1252":"1252","1340":"1340","1262":"1262","1382":"1382","1282":"1282","1328":"1328","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Strickland Ketel, Westmorland,